high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the table.
Take the large knife from the table.
Stay at the table.
Cut the lettuce into slices on the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf of the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the cut lettuce on the table.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge. Take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn right, go forward, turn right, take a step forward, turn around to face the lettuce on the table.
Put the lettuce slice to the left of the lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and face the table in front of you.
Take the knife from the table in front of you.
Face the lettuce on the table in front of you.
Slice the lettuce on the table in front of you.
Turn left then face the fridge on your right.
Place the knife inside of the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn right and face the table on your left.
Take a lettuce slice off of the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge on your right.
Place the lettuce inside of the fridge in front of you then take it out.
Turn right and face the table to your left.
Place the lettuce slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold lettuce slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Look down to the front of the table
Slice the lettuce on the table
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the table
Pick up a lettuce slice from the table
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the lettuce slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the lettuce slice from the fridge
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the table
Put the lettuce slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce, cool a slice
